OL,3,CFish and chip shop saves wedding as
OL,4,Ccaterers pull out a day before
OL,6,FAn award-winning fish and chip shop
OL,7,Fcame to the rescue of a Devon couple
OL,8,Fwho were let down by their wedding
OL,9,Fcaterer less than 24 hours before
OL,10,Ftheir big day.
OL,12,FIn a last-ditch attempt to help the
OL,13,Fcouple, the mother-of-the-bride rang
OL,14,FKrispies in Exmouth last Friday
OL,15,Fafternoon (7 June), to see if they
OL,16,Fcould serve up 110 portions of fish
OL,17,Fand chips for the next day.
OL,19,FKelly Barnes, who owns the chippy with
OL,20,Fher husband Tim, did not hesitate in
OL,21,Fcoming to their aid.
