OL,3,CFish and chip shop saves wedding as
OL,4,Ccaterers pull out a day before
OL,6,FThe couple, with the help of their
OL,7,Fstaff including some who worked
OL,8,Fovertime, successfully delivered the
OL,9,Fhuge order to the wedding venue at
OL,10,FPrattshayes Farm in Exmouth.
OL,12,FThe food went down a storm with the
OL,13,Fhappy couple and their guests.
OL,15,FKelly said: "When the mother of the
OL,16,Fbride rang there was trepidation as
OL,17,Fshe wanted to know how we would get
OL,18,F110 meals that were still hot to them
OL,19,Fin such a short space of time.
