OL,3,CFish and chip shop saves wedding as
OL,4,Ccaterers pull out a day before
OL,6,F"We do food for around five or six
OL,7,FStuart Line cruises a year so we are
OL,8,Fused to doing it and that is on a
OL,9,FFriday evening when we are busy so to
OL,10,Fdo it on a Saturday afternoon was
OL,11,Fquite pleasant as we are not so busy
OL,12,Fthen.
OL,14,F"It was just a pleasure to be able to
OL,15,Fhelp out. How could we not? Even if we
OL,16,Fwere busy we would have found a way of
OL,17,Fhelping them out as we are in a
OL,18,Fposition where we can do that. That's
OL,19,Fwhat we teach our staff and is how I
OL,20,Fwas raised.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
