OL,3,CFish and chip shop saves wedding as
OL,4,Ccaterers pull out a day before
OL,6,F"Luckily the wedding venue was just 10
OL,7,Fminutes up the road from our shop. Our
OL,8,Fteam were amazing and some stayed on
OL,9,Fafter their shift ended to help."
OL,11,FKelly added: "The bride and groom were
OL,12,Fvery sweet and thanked us before we
OL,13,Fleft and wedding guests also thanked
OL,14,Fus and asked us how the food was still
OL,15,Fhot when they got it.
OL,17,F"People think it's a big job but you
OL,18,Fjust have to make sure you have enough
OL,19,Fteam members.
