OL,3,CFish and chip shop saves wedding as
OL,4,Ccaterers pull out a day before
OL,6,F"As soon as the food was ready we had
OL,7,Fabout seven people wrapping the orders
OL,8,Fto get it out as quickly as possible."
OL,10,FKrispies opened its doors in Exmouth
OL,11,Fmore than 20 years ago. It now has two
OL,12,Fshops in the town on Exeter Road and
OL,13,FPines Road, and opened up its first
OL,14,Fshop in Exeter on Isleworth Road in
OL,15,F2022.
OL,17,FKripsies is renowned for its battered
OL,18,Fchips and has won numerous awards over
OL,19,Fthe years.
